  options = '[{"id":"A","text":"Genetic engineering has the potential to benefit society, but scientists must be careful not to use it in ways that are harmful or controversial.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"The author argues that while genetic engineering has the potential to improve society, scientists must proceed cautiously to avoid harmful or controversial applications of the technology.  The text mentions that the public''s distrust of genetic engineering is rooted in the potential risks of the tec. Choice A matches the question''s requirement and is consistent with the passage''s central claim or supporting detail. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"B","text":"The development of new biofuels and biodegradable plastics has increased public confidence in the safety of genetic engineering.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice B is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"C","text":"The public''s distrust of genetic engineering is unfounded, because genetic engineering has the potential to lead to many breakthroughs in medicine.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice C is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."},{"id":"D","text":"Scientists are working to develop new ways to use genetic engineering in medicine that are not controversial.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"This choice does not follow from the information given or contains a calculation error. Choice D is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."}]'::jsonb,
